        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -30,
          "y_px": -407
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-8",
        "text": "In the spring of 2018, after days of relentless rain, a 100 foot section of this iconic wall",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -8,
          "y_px": -188
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-10",
        "text": "collapsed. Though constructed in the mid-1800s as part of a major public works",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -6,
          "y_px": -120
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "project, officials deemed its restoration a private undertaking. The considerable debris",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -6,
          "y_px": -52
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "was then cleared by one man and a wheelbarrow. Design of a stone faced concrete",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 6,
          "y_px": 10
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "retaining wall with a plan to build it was developed by a friend. Months of community",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 8,
          "y_px": 76
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-19",
        "text": "spirited fundraising followed along with two years of construction by immigrants",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -70,
          "y_px": 144
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-24",
        "text": "skilled in use of concrete, steel and stone. The man was Edward &apos;Sandy&apos; Feddema,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -34,
          "y_px": 210
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-26",
        "text": "property co-owner. His friend Jeffrey R. Fogg - civil engineer and region native -",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 274
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-29",
        "text": "managed the project. The two men - both in their seventies - together went on to scour",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 332
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-31",
        "text": "local sandpits and farms for additional giant ironstones, then lifted, cut, carted, shaped",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 389
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-33",
        "text": "and placed them to form a new upper wall and constructed new granite gabion baskets",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 447
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-35",
        "text": "to secure the original stairway. Completed in November 2021, these walls now stand",
